query:
SELECT
                number,
                pubdata_input,
                sealed_at
            FROM
                l1_batches
            LEFT JOIN
                data_availability
                ON data_availability.l1_batch_number = l1_batches.number
            WHERE
                number != 0
                AND data_availability.blob_id = $1
                AND pubdata_input IS NOT NULL
                AND sealed_at IS NOT NULL
            ORDER BY
                number
            LIMIT
                1
